roducts or services.Investment ManagementStoker Ostler professionals adhere to the portfolio theory developed by University of Chicago economist Harry M. Markowitz who won a Nobel Prize in economics in 1990. Like Markowitz, we believe that proper portfolio management incorporates an analysis of both the expected risks and returns, as measured statistically, to achieve optimum investment results.TaxesTax PlanningOur team of advisors stays abreast of changing tax laws and works closely with top tax professionals to ensure that your wealth plan incorporates appropriate and ethical tax planning.Estate TaxesTax ServicesIncome TaxSome of the areas we analyze may include: retirement planning, income tax planning, risk management, insurance planning, business succession, education funding and estate planning. Since we focus on your financial well-being, you have the freedom to focus on other personal priorities. We look forward to learning your aspirations and developing a strategy to achieve them. Just give us a call, and we'll set up a time that's convenient for you.Send to PhoneStoker Ostler Wealth Advisors4900 N Scottsdale Rd, Scottsdale, AZ 85251(480) 890-8088Send this business listing as a text message to a mobile phone.I agree to the Terms and ConditionsCancelSendYour text message was sent.To opt out at anytime, send the word STOP to YP411.To get a help message, send the word HELP to YP411.There was an error sending your text.Please try again.E-MailStoker Ostler Wealth Advisors4900 N Scottsdale Rd, Scottsdale, AZ 85251(480) 890-8088Send this business details to yourself or up to 5 friends.Up to 5 email addresses, separate addresses with a commaSend Yourself a CopyCancelSend 
